main_desc.message: Open source, small plugins that enhance the functionality of new tabs. Quickly search bookmarks, history. You can easily manage your browsing history and block some useless records on the google search page.

msg_more.message: More records not shown, please narrow your search

msg_toomuch.message: Exceeded limit (500), no more site settings can be recorded

group_nohistory.message: Delete site record & no longer record

group_black.message: Delete site record & no longer record & disable on google search

newtab_search.message: Search from bookmarks and records (press Enter)

google_disable_msg.message: This site has been blocked by you (Web Record Manager)
